{"type": "article", "id": 12879, "title": "白色大理石和墨绿色座椅是绝配，看这个甜品店就知道了", "description": "眼睛和胃都能满足！\r\n", "date": "2015-07-31T11:38:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12872, "name": "墨尔本"}, {"id": 13798, "name": "甜品店"}, {"id": 13799, "name": "店铺装修"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 159, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021047038HTlSpOq6hxdycZv.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t位于澳大利亚墨尔本的这家甜品店，室内的装修设计把极简风发挥到了极致——意大利工艺的智能橱柜、墨绿色的座椅、白理石的收银台——在这些装饰下，巧克力和慕斯蛋糕显得熠熠生辉。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t甜品店的室内设计是由墨尔本本土工作室 Breathe Architecture 完成的，每周四到周日，店铺都供应下午茶，包含椰子杏仁、覆盆子和荔枝慕斯等，马卡龙也有多种口味，由当地原料制成。除了甜品，店内还供应香槟和礼品包装的巧克力、坚果和饼干，临走时，你还可以买走本地生产的蜂蜜、茶和咖啡，估计来店的整天都不用吃主食了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021047007cAuG2gIQWsmEkfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这家甜品店位于墨尔本\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104700NfSH6jizF3evsyqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t甜品展架<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104701ct7SdLu4gpmywH9b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t产品货架\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021047015zlIBkHRTmixgrLn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t从远处看\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104701NFTWHiqu0RDQxUzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t甜品店的正门\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104702saLF2qy9KmNk0Gt4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t诱人甜品<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210470212B84IGDmWwcvSkP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t座椅区的风格对比\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/lifestyle/sweet-sensation-bibelots-dessert-boutique-opens-in-south-melbourne/9349#124440\" target=\"_blank\"><em>wallpaper</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}